xternal text" href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/w/index.php?title=Special%3AUploadWizard&amp;categories=Buzz+Aldrin">Upload media</a></b></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" style="text-align:center; font-weight:bold"><div><span typeof="mw:File"><span><img alt="" src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/80/Wikipedia-logo-v2.svg/20px-Wikipedia-logo-v2.svg.png" decoding="async" width="16" height="15" class="mw-file-element" srcset="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/80/Wikipedia-logo-v2.svg/40px-Wikipedia-logo-v2.svg.png 1.5x" data-file-width="103" data-file-height="94" /></span></span>&#160;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Buzz_Aldrin" class="extiw" title="en:Buzz Aldrin">Wikipedia</a></div><div><span typeof="mw:File"><span><img alt="" src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fa/Wikiquote-logo.svg/20px-Wikiquote-logo.svg.png" decoding="async" width="13" height="16" class="mw-file-element" srcset="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fa/Wikiquote-logo.svg/40px-Wikiquote-logo.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="300" data-file-height="355" /></span></span>&#160;<a href="https://en.wikiquote.org/wiki/en:Buzz_Aldrin" class="extiw" title="q:en:Buzz Aldrin">Wikiquote</a></div><div><span typeof="mw:File"><span><img alt="" src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/24/Wikinews-logo.svg/20px-Wikinews-logo.svg.png" decoding="async" width="16" height="9" class="mw-file-element" srcset="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/24/Wikinews-logo.svg/40px-Wikinews-logo.svg.png 1.5x" data-file-width="759" data-file-height="415" /></span></span>&#160;<a href="https://en.wikinews.org/wiki/en:Category:Buzz_Aldrin" class="extiw" title="n:en:Category:Buzz Aldrin">Wikinews</a></div></td></tr><tr class="wdinfo&#95;nomobile"><th class="wikidatainfobox-lcell">Name in native language</th><td><div class="plainlist"><ul><li>Edwin Eugene Aldrin Jr.</li></ul></div></td></tr><tr class="wdinfo&#95;nomobile"><th class="wikidatainfobox-lcell">Date of birth</th><td>20 January 1930<br />Mountainside Medical Center<br />Edwin Eugene Aldrin</td></tr><tr class="wdinfo&#95;nomobile"><th class="wikidatainfobox-lcell">Country of citizenship</th><td><div class="plainlist"><ul><li><a href="/wiki/United_States" title="United States">United States</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr class="wdinfo&#95;nomobile"><th class="wikidatainfobox-lcell">Educated at</th><td><div class="plainlist"><ul><li><a href="/wiki/Category:Massachusetts_Institute_of_Technology" title="Category:Massachusetts Institute of Technology">Massachusetts Institute of Technology</a> (Doctor of Science, <a href="/wiki/Astronautics" title="Astronautics">astronautics</a>)</li><li><a href="/wiki/United_States_Military_Academy" title="United States Military Academy">United States Military Academy</a> (Bachelor of Science)</li><li><a href="/wiki/Category:Severn_School" title="Category:Severn School">Severn School</a></li><li>Montclair High School</li></ul></div></td></tr><tr class="wdinfo&#95;nomobile"><th class="wikidatainfobox-lcell">Doctoral advisor</th><td><div class="plainlist"><ul><li>Walter Wrigley</li><li>Myron A. Hoffman</li><li>Robert L. Halfman</li><li>Norman E. Sears</li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th class="wikidatainfobox-lcell">Occupation</th><td><div class="plainlist"><ul><li><a href="/wiki/Category:Air_force_officers" title="Category:Air force officers">air force officer</a></li><li><a href="/wiki/Category:Fighter_pilots" title="Category:Fighter pilots">fighter pilot</a></li><li><a href="/wiki/Category:Astronauts" title="Category:Astronauts">astronaut</a></li><li><a href="/wiki/Category:Autobiographers" title="Category:Autobiographers">autobiographer</a></li><li><a href="/wiki/Category:Science_fiction_writers" title="Category:Science fiction writers">science fiction writer</a></li><li><a href="/wiki/Category:Engineers" title="Category:Engineers">engineer</a></li><li><a href="/wiki/Category:Businesspeople" title="Category:Businesspeople">businessman</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr class="wdinfo&#95;nomobile"><th class="wikidatainfobox-lcell">Employer</th><td><div class="plainlist"><ul><li><a href="/wiki/NASA" title="NASA">National Aeronautics and Space Administration</a> (<a href="/wiki/Category:Astronauts" title="Category:Astronauts">astronaut</a>)</li></ul></div></td></tr><tr class="wdinfo&#95;nomobile"><th class="wikidatainfobox-lcell">Member of</th><td><div class="plainlist"><ul><li>International Academy of Astronautics</li></ul></div></td></tr><tr class="wdinfo&#95;nomobile"><th class="wikidatainfobox-lcell">Member of political party</th><td><div class="plainlist"><ul><li><a href="/wiki/Republican_Party_(United_States)" title="Republican Party (United States)">Republican Party</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr class="wdinfo&#95;nomobile"><th class="wikidatainfobox-lcell">Significant event</th><td><div class="plainlist"><ul><li>walk on the Moon (9,060 second, 1969&#8211;1969)</li></ul></div></td></tr><tr class="wdinfo&#95;nomobile"><th class="wikidatainfobox-lcell">Father</th><td><div class="plainlist"><ul><li><a href="/wiki/Category:Edwin_Eugene_Aldrin_Sr." title="Category:Edwin Eugene Aldrin Sr.">Edwin Eugene Aldrin Sr.</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr class="wdinfo&#95;nomobile"><th class="wikidatainfobox-lcell">Mother</th><td><div class="plainlist"><ul><li>Marion Gladys Moon</li></ul></div></td></tr><tr class="wdinfo&#95;nomobile"><th class="wikidatainfobox-lcell">Spouse</th><td><div class="plainlist"><ul><li>Joan Ann Archer (1954&#8211;1974)</li><li>Beverly Van Zile (1975&#8211;1978)</li><li><a href="/wiki/Category:Lois_Driggs_Cannon" title="Category:Lois Driggs Cannon">Lois Driggs Cannon</a> (1988&#8211;2012)</li><li>Anca Faur (2023&#8211;2025)</li></ul></div></td></tr><tr class="wdinfo&#95;nomobile"><th class="wikidatainfobox-lcell">Award received</th><td><div class="mw-collapsible mw-collapsed" style="width:100%; overflow:auto;" data-expandtext="Show"